    .docs-content.with-device
      .full-width
        h1 Chips
        p.material-only Chips are supported only in Material Theme
        p Chips represent complex entities in small blocks, such as a contact. They can contain a photo, short title string, and brief information.
        h2 Chips HTML Layout
        p Let's look at basic chip HTML layout
        pre
          code
            | &lt;div class="chip"&gt;
            |     &lt;div class="chip-media"&gt;
            |         &lt;img src="http://lorempixel.com/100/100/people/9/"&gt;
            |     &lt;/div&gt;
            |     &lt;div class="chip-label"&gt;Jane Doe&lt;/div&gt;
            |     &lt;a href="#" class="chip-delete"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
            | &lt;/div&gt;
        p Where
        ul
          li
            p <code>&lt;div class="chip"&gt;</code> - Chip container
            ul
              li
                p <code>&lt;div class="chip-media"&gt;</code> - Chip "media" element, can contain image/avatar or icon. Optional
              li
                p <code>&lt;div class="card-label"&gt;</code> - Chip text label
              li
                p <code>&lt;a class="card-delete"&gt;</code> - Chip delete icon-link. Optional

